solaris service
command

1. start service
ex:
svcadm enable -r telnet
-r will recursively enables its  dependencies
-------------------------------------------------------------

2. check service status
(1) svcs
    show all service
(2) svcs | grep nfs
-------------------------------------------------------------
    
3. stop service
ex:
svcadm disable netatalk
-------------------------------------------------------------
4. startup script:
location:
/lib/svc/method/

-------------------------------------------------------------
startup script log:
location:
/var/svc/log & /etc/svc/volatile






